<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-930-272  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 930 272.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>UNIX World  Nov 1989 v6 n11 p115(3).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Sophisticated project management. (Aide-de-Camp project managementsoftware) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Taylor, Dave.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Software Maintenance and Development System has launched version7.0 of its Aide-de-Camp project management system.andP;  The latestversion is fast, full-featured but very difficult to learn.andP;  Theprogram has very poor documentation and insufficient tutorials forthe user.andP;  Aide-de-Camp is designed to ease the organization ofadministrative duties surrounding a project.andP;  It complies with DODstandard 2167A for software design and development projects.andP;  Theprogram comes with a simple English macro scripting language.andO;Aide-de-camp runs on a number of minicomputer and workstationplatforms.andP;  Pricing varies according to the platform but usuallyis around $1,000 for a basic program.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Software Maintenance and Development Systems Inc. (products).andO;Product:   Aide-de-Camp (Project management software).andO;Topic:     Project Management SystemsProgrammingTrainingEvaluation.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>